result.title: Blaxites
result.description:
Jai's celebratory social media post affects her access to vital medication. Her attempts to circumvent the system leads to even more dire consequences.

The Surveillance Studies Center and the Big Data Surveillance Project present A Screening Surveillance Film. For more information, visit: https://www.screeningsurveillance.com/.

Written by: Nehal El-Hadi
Directed by: Josh Lyon
